{"tid":750991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國3間航空公司未按中國要求整改對台灣標注","createTime":"2018-07-21T12:40:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-22T02:27:07.000Z","uid":141151,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ed8b1b50b17c202e7e5a2b2e1320c953758c6ff2","tid":750991,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:40:41.000Z","msg":"美國3間航空公司未按中國要求整改對台灣標注<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1020466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3Fcsid%3D261_367%26itemid%3D1020466&d=6bvjaSOZCT5YRZrG%2BCcGUozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5fa5505c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?csid=261_367&amp;itemid=1020466</a><br />\n<br />\n中國民航局要求44間外國航空公司，下星期三前完成整改對台灣及港澳地區的錯誤標注，目前仍有6間航空公司未完成整改，包括3間美國的航空公司。其中，達美航空表示，正在審查中國民航局的要求，並持續與美國政府保持密切磋商。美國航空亦指，正就事件與美國政府磋商。英國《金融時報》引述知情人士指，美國官員已要求達美、美航及聯合航空，不要聽從中國的要求，修改網站和地圖上對台灣的標注。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，外交部日前表示，外國企業在中國的經營活動，應當尊重中國的主權和領土完整，遵守中國法律法規，重申一個中國是基本事實，亦是國際共識。"},{"pid":"ed0f573823fd0566f4feaddb7341ebe91cef36b5","tid":750991,"uid":53466,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:41:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"902f38b18ea2e18cfe933fad682eb7429ea0810c","tid":750991,"uid":61280,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:43:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">支狗強項：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面人地唔俾，架自己先丟！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"12c486e2fd4bedb34d00f68ce3974310f5cfb8ce","tid":750991,"uid":67655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"世界都是中國的<img src=\"/